{
  "stem": "10353.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I was already up in the higher, higher studies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But It was very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And naturally, poverty arraigned all around us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And not only that it was a universal depression, but being Jewish, and although there were some very prominent and wealthy Jews in our community, but the vast, vast majority lived in real poverty.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the Jewish community was very, very active and helped the poor people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To a great extent, they had the-- the Romanian government gave the Jewish leadership, the so-called congress gave them vast powers to tax and to assess members, those that could afford it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And consequently, they could help out, to some extent, the very poor people, the widows, the orphans, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had some very, very good organizations, their own hospital, Jewish hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had orphanages.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had [NON-ENGLISH], Hadassahs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a well-organized community.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was all very good until 1939.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Needless to say, prior to 1939, we had the-- the saber rattlings of the war was constantly in the picture.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we knew very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we, not only through newspapers, we were very, very well-informed of what was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] We were very, very knowledgeable about the rising of the Hitler era.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my father went for medical reasons, went to Berlin in 1931.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came back in 1932.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember, as a-- as a kid, that he told us the story that there is some movement in Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there's this fellow by the name of Hitler that, if he comes to power, then it will be the demise-- it will be the demise of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember, it was like a story, you know, that-- that you hear.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
